  <name>ioquake3</name>
  <summary>Free and open-source Quake 3 based engine</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ioquake3 is a free and open-source software first person shooter engine
      based on the Quake 3: Arena and Quake 3: Team Arena source code.
    </p>
    <p>
      The source code is licensed under the GPL version 2, and was first
      released under that license by id software on August 20th, 2005. Since
      then, our dedicated team has been working hard to improve it, fixing bugs,
      and adding just the right new features to make the engine even better than
      before.
    </p>
  </description>
